(51, 50, 'Stainless', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', 'Center Hole Config.jpg', 0),
(52, 51, 'L type', '1', '1', '1', 'LType_1.png', '<p>L-type blades provides the most intense tillage and the best cutting &amp; mixing of crop residues, manure etc. Made from a special grade of Boron allow steel, with a minimum hardness of 50 + 2 HRC our blades guarantee uniform hardness insuring superior performance and long life. No matter the soil type, soil conditions or the amount of residue, our blades will always give the best result.</p>', '<table class="diameter" style="width: 100%;" border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE DISTANCE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 6</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Center Hole Config.jpg', 0),
(53, 51, 'C type', '1', '1', '0', 'CType_2.png', '<p>C-type blades require less power and provide a coarser finish for better moisture penetration. Made from a special grade of Boron allow steel, with a minimum hardness of 50 + 2 HRC our blades guarantee uniform hardness insuring superior performance and long life. No matter the soil type, soil conditions or the amount of residue, our blades will always give the best result.</p>', '<table class="diameter" style="width: 100%;" border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE DISTANCE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 6</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Center Hole Config.jpg', 0),
(54, 51, 'J type', '0', '0', '1', 'JType_1.png', '<p>J-type blades are the most versatile solution, the multi purpose choice. &nbsp;Made from a special grade of Boron allow steel, with a minimum hardness of 50 + 2 HRC our blades guarantee uniform hardness insuring superior performance and long life. No matter the soil type, soil conditions or the amount of residue, our blades will always give the best result.</p>', '<table class="diameter" style="width: 100%;" border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>HOLE DISTANCE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>80 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 8</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 7</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>70 X 6</strong></td>\r\n<td>11.5,12.5,13.5,14,5</td>\r\n<td>46,57</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Center Hole Config.jpg', 0),
